lead_paragraph: Golden State Warriors guard Stephen Curry slipped on a wet spot late in the first half and limped to the locker room at halftime of Game Four against the Houston Rockets.

headline.print_headline: Golden State Guard Curry Misses Second Half With Knee Strain
